Description: rOzCBI contains background, digital data capture, analysis, and
             visualisation for the calculation of OzCBI, a composite burn index
             for the initial assessment of the short-term burn severity from
             remotely sensed data.
URL: https://dbca-wa.github.io/rOzCBI, https://github.com/dbca-wa/rOzCBI, https://dbca-wa.github.io/rOzCBI/
